      "text": "TARIFFS AND RATE SCHEDULES\n\n##### Search Oncor\n\nType your question or choose from the quick topics to view generative AI results from Search Oncor.\n\n##### Most Searched Questions\n\nIs the Outage Map in real-time? Does Oncor automatically know when my power is out? How do I report power outage?\n\n---\n\n##### Quick Links\n\nDownload MyOncor Mobile App\n\nTo Report Outage via text : Text “OUT” to 66267\n\nTo Receive MyOncor Alerts : Text “REG” to 66267\n\n- Report Outage\n- Check Status\n- View Outage Map\n- Sign Up For MyOncor Alerts\n\n##### Search Oncor\n\nType your question or choose from the quick topics to view generative AI results from Search Oncor.\n\n##### Most Searched Questions\n\nIs the Outage Map in real-time? Does Oncor automatically know when my power is out? How do I report power outage?\n\n---\n\n##### Quick Links\n\nDownload MyOncor Mobile App\n\nTo Report Outage via text : Text “OUT” to 66267\n\nTo Receive MyOncor Alerts : Text “REG” to 66267\n\n- /ug+/content/oncorwww/us/en/home/faqs/faqs-details.html#faq-tabs-item-0dc0758cfb-tab\n- /moafaq+/content/oncorwww/us/en/home/faqs/faqs-details.html#faq-tabs-item-bd6b8432a1-tab\n- /solarfaq+/content/oncorwww/us/en/home/faqs/faqs-details.html#faq-tabs-item-efa19cdf21-tab\n- /meterfaq+/content/oncorwww/us/en/home/faqs/faqs-details.html#faq-tabs-item-49af93d268-tab\n- /mapfaq+/content/oncorwww/us/en/home/faqs/faqs-details.html#faq-tabs-item-ca0e726e43-tab\n- /stlgtfaq+/content/oncorwww/us/en/home/faqs/faqs-details.html#faq-tabs-item-f80ab6a786-tab\n\n# TARIFFS AND RATE SCHEDULES\n\n## TARIFFS AND RATE SCHEDULES\n\nOncor provides full transparency about our pricing, with various rates and schedules, including applicable riders. All rates and charges are approved by the Public Utility Commission of Texas (PUCT) and the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission (FERC), if applicable.\n\n### TARIFF FOR RETAIL DELIVERY SERVICE\n\nOncor's retail delivery service rate schedules and applicable riders include detailed information on retail pricing as approved by the PUCT.\n\nFilename Tariff for Retail Delivery Service.pdf\n\nSize 3 MB\n\nFormat application/pdf\n\n### ONCOR RETAIL DELIVERY SERVICE RATE CODES\n\nThis downloadable file is a complete list of Oncor Retail Delivery Service Rate Codes. The codes are applicable to all retail electric providers (REP) receiving delivery service within Oncor's service area.\n\nFilename Rate Codes Info.pdf\n\nSize 75 KB\n\nFormat application/pdf\n\n### RESIDENTIAL DELIVERY SERVICE RATE COMPARISON\n\nCompare Oncor delivery service rates to other transmission and distribution service providers.\n\n### WHOLESALE TRANSMISSION SERVICE TARIFFS\n\nTransmission Service tariffs apply to wholesale transmission service within ERCOT and are approved by the PUCT. The tariffs comply with the Texas Utilities Code and PUCT Substantive Rule requirements that wholesale open access transmission service be provided on a nondiscriminatory basis to all wholesale transmission system users, including the company itself.\n\nFilename Transmission Tariff.pdf\n\nSize 1 MB\n\nFormat application/pdf\n\nFilename Oncor NTU Tariff for Transmission Service.pdf\n\nSize 1 MB\n\nFormat application/pdf\n\n### FERC TFO TARIFF\n\nThe Tariff for Transmission Service To, From and Over Certain HVDC Interconnections (FERC TFO Tariff) applies to wholesale transmission service, which utilizes the North or East HVDC interconnections between ERCOT and the Southwest Power Pool (SPP). This tariff is approved by the FERC.\n\nFilename FERC TFO TARIFF.pdf\n\nSize 319 KB\n\nFormat application/pdf\n\nReport power outage\n\nClick here for More Details.\n\nMyOncor Alerts\n\nDownload Our App\n\n### Follow Us\n\n### download our app\n\n#### What We Do\n\n##### Safety\n\n##### Economic Development\n\n##### External Affairs\n\n##### Regulatory\n\n##### Transmission System\n\n##### Electric Distribution System\n\n##### Advanced Metering Service\n\n#### PARTNERS\n\n##### REP Resources\n\n##### Supplier Diversity\n\n##### Energy Efficiency Contractors\n\n##### Tree Pruning Contractors\n\n#### Smart Energy\n\n##### Electric Vehicles\n\n##### Renewables, Solar & More\n\n##### Energy Efficiency Programs\n\n#### MORE\n\n##### Careers\n\n##### Investor Relations\n\n##### News | The Wire\n\n##### Brand Standards\n\n##### FAQ's\n\n#### Contact us\n\n##### General Inquiries\n\n### (888) 313 6862\n\n##### Media Inquiries\n\n### (877) 426 1616\n\n##### Power Outages\n\n### (888) 313 4747\n\n##### Locate Underground Power Lines\n\n### 811\n\n#### Quick Links\n\n###### Social Media & Web House Rules\n\n##### Privacy\n\n###### Terms & Conditions\n\n###### Copyright Policy\n\n###### Español\n\n---\n\n###### social media & web house rules\n\n###### Privacy\n\n###### terms & conditions\n\n###### copyright policy\n\n###### español\n\n© 2026 Oncor Electric Delivery Company LLC. All rights reserved.",
